# UI/UX Design System & Patterns

## Design Philosophy

This project follows a clean, minimalist design inspired by modern SaaS platforms like Linear, Vercel, Craft, and Stripe. The design emphasizes clarity, accessibility, and a professional aesthetic while maintaining the platform's unique identity.

